## What It Does

Remember those memory card games you played as a kid? This is that, but with a sleek poker table design. Flip cards, find matching pairs, and try to beat your best score. Simple concept, surprisingly addictive.

## Features

- **30 cards to match** - Find all 15 pairs to win
- **Score tracking** - Your best scores are saved locally (lower is better!)
- **Timer & move counter** - See how fast and efficient you can be
- **Pause/Resume** - Take a break without losing your progress
- **How to Play guide** - Auto-shows for first-time players
- **Fully responsive** - Works great on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- **Poker table theme** - Because everything looks cooler with a felt background

